    <item>
      <title>在北京领导的镇压下，美国制裁更多的香港官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-sanctions-more-hong-kong-officials-amid-beijing-led-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府正在批准六名香港官员，包括该市司法部长和警察专员，以针对实施北京强硬政策的当局的最新步骤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-sanctions-more-hong-kong-officials-amid-beijing-led-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 17:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博茨瓦纳寻求新的Eskom电力协议，因为供应危机加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/botswana-seeks-new-eskom-power-deal-as-supply-crisis-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波茨瓦纳的政府官员将在电力投资人翻了一番以上后，本周将与南非的电力部会面，从而恶化供应危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/botswana-seeks-new-eskom-power-deal-as-supply-crisis-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 16:03:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普媒体将首先列出纽约证交所的德克萨斯州哨所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-media-will-become-first-listing-for-nyse-s-texas-outpost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的媒体企业正在与德克萨斯州建立象征性的联系，成为第一家在纽约证券交易所（New York Stock Exchange）在孤星州的新兴前哨基地列出的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-media-will-become-first-listing-for-nyse-s-texas-outpost</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 15:45:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曼德拉（Mandela）的继任者姆贝基（Mbeki）说，他是种族隔离案的目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/mandela-s-successor-mbeki-says-he-s-target-of-apartheid-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[接替纳尔逊·曼德拉（Nelson Mandela）成为民主南非的第二任总统的塔博·姆贝基（Thabo Mbeki）在政府与种族隔离时代犯罪受害者家属之间犯下了合法的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/mandela-s-successor-mbeki-says-he-s-target-of-apartheid-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 15:42:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股票下跌，随着恐惧在特朗普的关税之前的恐惧而获得的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-stocks-swoon-as-trump-sows-economic-fear-across-wall-street</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，周一，唐纳德·特朗普总统下一次关税推出将颠覆全球经济，随着投资者转移到诸如财政债券和黄金等避风港之际，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trund）下一次关税将升级，市场再次震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-stocks-swoon-as-trump-sows-economic-fear-across-wall-street</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 13:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
